title.es: My food’s cold again. Knew it.

comment.en: Nature’s efficiency often makes my own multi-tasking feel rather…inept.
comment.es: La naturaleza me hace ver... torpe.
comment.pt-BR: Natureza eficiente. Meu esforço é meio... assim.

title.en: Starting my break. Just another countdown.
title.es: Still here. Of course I am.

comment.en: They seem to get more done with less effort than I manage most mornings.
comment.es: Parecen rendir más con menos esfuerzo que yo.
comment.pt-BR: Eles rendem mais com menos. Eu, sou... eu.

title.en: Food getting cold. What did I expect?
title.pt-BR: My food's cold. It's fine. I don't deserve it hot.

comment.en: It’s impressive how some creatures adapt, while I still struggle with the projector.
comment.es: Qué habilidad para adaptarse... Y yo, con el proyector.
comment.pt-BR: Bichos evoluem. Eu, com o projetor, nem tanto.
